==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī jǔ liǎng dé

===Etymology===
Literally: One action, two gains.

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[举]][[两]][[得]]'''

# [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals.

===Alternate forms===
[[一舉兩得]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

[[一挙両得]] ([[Japanese]])

===Related terms===
*[[一箭双雕]]
*[[一石二鸟]]

